{"tid":579343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"住公屋呢啲樓底薄嘅窮人樓至驟忌就係自己單位對上有細蚊仔住！","createTime":"2018-03-03T13:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T14:08:06.000Z","uid":120980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"021d95a843acecca814ed62dbfdee1dcd39cdc2e","tid":579343,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:42:39.000Z","msg":"唔知樓上果戶冚家祥家庭係新入伙定啲細蚊仔進入活躍時期<br />\n<br />\n以前不論晝夜都好寧靜 但係由新春期間至今 除非樓上啲人出晒街或訓晒覺<br />\n<br />\n否則拉凳聲 暴龍腳步聲 跌野落地聲 揼野聲呢啲都走唔甩<br />\n<br />\n仲要久唔久響你一下又應聲果度先攞命<br />\n<br />\n曾經門鐘又㩒過 樓下大堂又投訴過<br />\n<br />\n當然兩次樓上都唔認然後繼續<br />\n<br />\n我終於明白神經衰弱果種滋味係點<br />\n<br />\n啲人真係好撚冇公德 枉為人父母<br />\n<br />\n再積多些小怨氣真係某朝你地就會有新聞睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c26a97812f8e9d7464eee95f99ad16a8ca075972","tid":579343,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"你確定樓上有人住？"},{"pid":"e24ba2bb0144efc944026e1e7b1f54bce5a8d4ec","tid":579343,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71d2b7babe839472ae7cc134df29166f57eaaf61","tid":579343,"uid":120980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c26a97812f8e9d7464eee95f99ad16a8ca075972","tid":579343,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:47:34.000Z","msg":"你確定樓上有人住？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"我14樓<br />\n<br />\n對上15樓<br />\n<br />\n曾經㩒過門鐘有人開門<br />\n<br />\n親眼見到一家有四口<br />\n<br />\nE家對上仲有著燈<br />\n<br />\n除非我見鬼"},{"pid":"96c336363235b53ba5694a9bbed9fcdf6fa5c7d8","tid":579343,"uid":120980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e24ba2bb0144efc944026e1e7b1f54bce5a8d4ec","tid":579343,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"洗閪你教"},{"pid":"a4741b07625afa1b2e2c0518819ee30b12d188db","tid":579343,"ui